@startuml
actor Etudiant
participant ReservationsController
participant ReservationService
participant SalleDAO
participant ReservationDAO
participant NotificationService

Etudiant -> ReservationsController : saisir salle + créneau + motif
ReservationsController -> ReservationService : creerReservation(etudiant, salle, debut, fin)

ReservationService -> SalleDAO : findById(salleId)
SalleDAO --> ReservationService : Salle

ReservationService -> ReservationDAO : verifierDisponibilite(salle, debut, fin)
ReservationDAO --> ReservationService : disponible / non disponible

alt disponible
    ReservationService -> ReservationDAO : save(statut = EN_ATTENTE)
    ReservationService -> NotificationService : notifier étudiant
    ReservationService --> ReservationsController : réservation créée
else conflit de créneau
    ReservationService --> ReservationsController : erreur disponibilité
end

@enduml
